Text: Note from original seeder: STOSSEL shows prior to 20100415 have been moved to offline storage. The peer pools are large enough to maintain seeding without me, after up ratios of over 50:1. IF seeds dry up and you want a re-seed of these older shows, your best chance is to make your request in the comments of the most recent show...and I'll be happy to re-seed. Thanks!
Note for STOSSEL of 2010, June 3, Thursday: A repeat of the "Road to Serfdom" episode of 20100211 aired, so no new show this week.
